  <brief_title>Combination of Continuous Femoral Block and Intravenous Parecoxib For Postoperative Analgesia After Total Knee Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>COMBINATION OF CONTINUOUS FEMORAL BLOCK AND INTRAVENOUS PARECOXIB FOR POSTOPERATIVE ANALGESIA AFTER TOTAL KNEE ARTHROPLASTY. A DOUBLE BLIND PROSPECTIVE STUDY.</official_title>
